text: Benipur Multilateral High School is a secondary school in Shailkupa Upazila, Jhenaidah District. It was established in 1906. This school has 2 academic (2 story) buildings, 1 student hostel, 1 mosque, and a library. ==References== Category:Educational institutions established in 1906 Category:High schools in Bangladesh Category:Schools in Jhenaidah District Category:1906 establishments in India
